comments: He will remain forever in the memory of jazz musicians and jazz fans.
THE TRANE

Divine intervention? Call it nothing more than simple coincidence to wake from this Autumn’s slumber to this track playing. A vision; more, an essence of what and was:  conjured unlike any I've had in quite a while. I wonder what sort of night lies ahead. [11pm, GMT -5]

No Give Me the Good Life, as in Life's Great.....see ya'
